BIB                 13         26
TITLE      Absorption of gamma quanta by manganese nuclei in the
            giant-resonance region.
AUTHOR     (B.S.Dolbilkin,A.I.Isakov,V.I.Korin,L.E.Lazareva)
INSTITUTE  (4RUSJIA)
REFERENCE  (J,JEL,10,231,1969)
            English translation of ZEP,10,365,1969.
           (J,ZEP,10,365,1969)
FACILITY   (SYNCH,4RUSLEB) 260 MeV synchrotron of FIAN.
INC-SOURCE (BRST)
SAMPLE     (25-MN-55,ENR=0.97) Alloy of manganese with copper
            (97% Mn - 3% Co).
DETECTOR   (BPAIR) 9-channel magnetic paired gamma spectrometer
            with resolution < 1%.
METHOD     (EXTB,SITA)
ANALYSIS   Photoabsorption cross   section   was   obtained   by
            subtraction of the atomic absorption  cross  section
            from   the  measured  sum  of  atomic   and  nuclear
            absorption cross sections.
REL-REF    (R,,K.Siegbahn,B,SIEGBAHN,,,1955)
            Atomic absorption  cross  section.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) Mean-root-squared uncertainties.
HISTORY    (20180402C) Data were compiled at the Russia MSU SINP
            CDFE by V.Varlamov.
           (20260423A) Corrected by V.Varlamov: TITLE,
            REFERENCE, SAMPLE, DETECTOR, REL-REF, REACTION,
            STATUS.
ENDBIB              26
